<note n="0876015" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0876015">青疑有</note>
<note n="0876016" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0876016">是或者乎又眾乎</note>
<note n="0877001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0877001">形或珠乎</note>
<note n="0877002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0877002">伽或作迦</note>
<note n="0878001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0878001">黎字非<g ref="#CB18835">󴦓</g>歟</note>
<note n="0878002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0878002">同字非可歟</note>
</p>
